floundered; tossed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shook, about,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to and fro; moved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, about,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to and fro,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from side to side; wabbled; wagged; quivered, quaked, trembled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shivered; fluttered; flickered;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tDr~b","text_ar":"تضرّب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same. (K. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, is sometimes used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHar~aka","text_ar":"تَحَرَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as mentioned before.]) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almawoju yaDoTaribu","text_ar":"المَوْجُ يَضْطَرِبُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The waves"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dash together, are tumultuous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beat one another."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb Alwaladu biAlbaToni","text_ar":"اضطرب الوَلَدُ بِالبَطْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The child was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a state of commotion in the belly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (A;) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY","text_ar":"فِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tDr~b","text_ar":"تضرّب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaToni","text_ar":"البَطْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which means the same]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb Albaroqu fiY Als~aHaAbi","text_ar":"اضطرب البَرْقُ فِى السَّحَابِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lightning was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, in a state of commotion in the clouds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it flickered therein;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHar~aka","text_ar":"تَحَرَّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb fiY A^umuwrihi","text_ar":"اضطرب فِى اُمُورِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went to and fro occupied in his affairs for the means of subsistence:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb","text_ar":"اضطرب"},{"kind":"text","text":", alone, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sought to gain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"applied himself with art and diligence to gain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aikotasaba","text_ar":"اِكْتَسَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) and is used by ElKumeyt with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almajoda","text_ar":"المَجْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as its objective complement. (TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaDoribu Almajoda","text_ar":"يَضْرِبُ المَجْدَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the latter half of the first paragraph.]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb Alr~ajulu","text_ar":"اضطرب الرَّجُلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The man was tall, and therewithal loose, lax, flabby, uncompact, slack,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shaky, in make,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"frame."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb Haboluhumo","text_ar":"اضطرب حَبْلُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their rope was shaky, loose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slack;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their word,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sentence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying, varied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was discordant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their words,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sayings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conflicted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"varied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were discordant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqowaAluhumo","text_ar":"اَقْوَالُهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"their sayings"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Kull p. 56.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb raA^oyuhu","text_ar":"اضطرب رَاْيُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His opinion was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, confused, weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsound"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rx","text_ar":"رخ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb Eaqoluhu","text_ar":"اضطرب عَقْلُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intellect, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, disordered, confused,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsound"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twh","text_ar":"توه"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb A^amoruhu","text_ar":"اضطرب اَمْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, disordered, unsound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K; *) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aixotal~a","text_ar":"اِخْتَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became unsound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unsettled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is indicated in the TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zl","text_ar":"زل"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrbt AlA^umuwru","text_ar":"اضطربت الاُمُورُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The affairs were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, complicated, intricate, confused, discordant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"incongruous;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aixotalafat","text_ar":"اِخْتَلَفَت"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb AlA^amoru bayonahumo","text_ar":"اضطرب الاَمْرُ بَيْنَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, complicated, intricate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confused, so as to be a subject of disagreement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difference, between them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajara","text_ar":"شَجَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb xaAtamFA","text_ar":"اضطرب خَاتَمًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He asked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ordered, that a signet-ring should be made, fashioned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"moulded, for him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA: [see also 4:]) occurring in a trad. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ADTrb binaA='F fiY Almasojidi","text_ar":"اضطرب بِنَا=ءً فِى المَسْجِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs in a trad. as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set up a structure upon stakes driven into the ground in the mosque."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Mgh"]}]}}